  "instructions": [
    "heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "add garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add cannellini beans and cook for 2-3 minutes, until heated through.",
    "add lemon juice and stir to combine.",
    "add orecchiette pasta to the skillet and toss to combine with the cannellini beans and sauce.",
    "season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley and grated parmesan cheese.",
    "if using parmesan cheese, sprinkle on top just before serving."
